==Championship Final==
The Fraser Valley Venom (Western Division champions) defeated the Toronto Renegades (Eastern Division Champions) 20-14 in the Championship Final, played in [[Surrey, British Columbia]] on 28 July 2001.<ref name="results" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rugbycanada.ca/super|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20020206000656/http://www.rugbycanada.ca/super|title=2001 Season - Schedule|archivedate=2002-02-06|accessdate=2011-04-24|publisher=[[Rugby Canada]]}}</ref>
