{{Infobox football biography |name = Ahmed Mogni |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1991|10|10|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Paris]], France |height = {{height|m=1.75}}<ref name = "NFT"/> |position = [[Midfielder]] |currentclub = [[Athletic Club de Boulogne-Billancourt|Boulogne-Billancourt]] |clubnumber = |youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = |years1 = 2010–2012 |clubs1 = [[Athletic Club de Boulogne-Billancourt|Boulogne-Billancourt]] |caps1 = |goals1 = |years2 = 2012–2014 |clubs2 = [[Évry FC|Évry]] |caps2 = 42 |goals2 = 4 |years3 = 2014–2016 |clubs3 = [[Paris FC|Paris B]] |caps3 = 34 |goals3 = 12 |years4 = 2015–2016 |clubs4 = [[Paris FC|Paris]] |caps4 = 10 |goals4 = 1 |years5 = 2017– |clubs5 = [[Athletic Club de Boulogne-Billancourt|Boulogne-Billancourt]] |caps5 = 11 |goals5 = 2 |nationalyears1 = 2015– |nationalteam1 = [[Comoros national football team|Comoros]] |nationalcaps1 = 7 |nationalgoals1 = 0 |club-update = 02:05, 6 February 2018 (UTC) |ntupdate = 17:43, 16 April 2016 (UTC) }} '''Ahmed Mogni''' (born 10 October 1991) is a Comorian international [[association football|footballer]] who plays for French club [[Athletic Club de Boulogne-Billancourt]], as a [[midfielder]].
