{{Infobox football club | clubname = AS Arta | image = | image_size = | upright = | alt = | caption = | fullname = Association Sportive d'Arta | nickname = | short name = | founded = | dissolved = | American = | ground = <!-- or: stadium --> | capacity = | coordinates = | owntitle = <!--optional, default: Owner --> | owner = | chrtitle = <!--optional, default: Chairman --> | chairman = | mgrtitle = <!--optional, default: Manager --> | manager = | coach = | league = [[Djibouti Premier League]] | season = | position = | website = | kit_alt1 = | pattern_la1 = | pattern_b1 = | pattern_ra1 = | pattern_sh1 = | pattern_so1 = | leftarm1 = | body1 = | rightarm1 = | shorts1 = | socks1 = | pattern_name1 = <!--optional, default: Home colours --> | kit_alt2 = | pattern_la2 = | pattern_b2 = | pattern_ra2 = | pattern_sh2 = | pattern_so2 = | leftarm2 = | body2 = | rightarm2 = | shorts2 = | socks2 = | pattern_name2 = <!--optional, default: Away colours --> | kit_alt3 = | pattern_la3 = | pattern_b3 = | pattern_ra3 = | pattern_sh3 = | pattern_so3 = | leftarm3 = | body3 = | rightarm3 = | shorts3 = | socks3 = | pattern_name3 = <!--optional, default: Third colours --> | current = }} '''Association Sportive d'Arta''' (currently known as '''Arta/Solar7''' for sponsorship reasons) is a [[Association football|football]] club from [[Arta, Djibouti|Arta]], [[Djibouti]]. They played in the [[2017–18 Djibouti Premier League]].<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesd/dji2018.html#div1 Djibouti 2017/18], RSSSF.com</ref>
The club has previously been known AS CDE/Arta (when sponsored by [[Ethio-Djibouti Railways]] ({{lang-fr|Chemin de Fer Djibouto-Éthiopien (C.D.E.)}})<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesd/dji2016.html#div1 Djibouti 2015/16], RSSSF.com</ref> and Arta/SIHD (when sponsored by the International Hydrocarbon Society ({{lang-fr|Société internationale des hydrocarbures de Djibouti}})).<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesd/dji2017.html#div1 Djibouti 2016/17], RSSSF.com</ref> As of 2018, the club is known as Arta/Solar 7 due to sponsorship with Djibouti-based Solar power company Solar 7.
