The '''East Germany national handball team''' represented the former country of [[East Germany]] in international [[team handball]] competitions. They had eight appearances at the [[World Men's Handball Championship]]s, where they won silver medals in [[1970 World Men's Handball Championship|1970]] and [[1974 World Men's Handball Championship|1974]], and bronze medals in [[1978 World Men's Handball Championship|1978]] and [[1986 World Men's Handball Championship|1986]].

