'''Kaake Kamta''' is an [[Gilbertese language|I-Kiribati]] [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]. He represents Kiribati at [[Kiribati national football team|international level]].<ref name="NFT">{{cite web | url = http://www.national-football-teams.com/player/44723/Kaake_Kamta.html| title = Kaake Kamta | work= national-football-teams.com |publisher=National Football Teams| accessdate = 25 May 2013}}</ref>
==International career== Batiri played 3&nbsp;games at the [[Men's Football at the 2011 Pacific Games|2011 Pacific Games]], two 1-17 losses to [[Tahiti national football team|Tahiti]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oceaniafootball.com/ofc/News/ViewArticle/tabid/125/Article/b89f0e50-3f24-474e-a008-ad1dfa24757f/language/en-US/Default.aspx|title=Kiribati 1 - 17 Tahiti|author=|date=4 September 2011|work=oceaniafootball.com|publisher=Oceania Football Confederation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130210163625/http://www.oceaniafootball.com/ofc/News/ViewArticle/tabid/125/Article/b89f0e50-3f24-474e-a008-ad1dfa24757f/language/en-US/Default.aspx|archivedate=10 February 2013|deadurl=yes|accessdate=25 May 2013|df=}}</ref> and [[Papua New Guinea national football team|Papua New Guinea]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oceaniafootball.com/ofc/News/ViewArticle/tabid/125/Article/22e56dd4-4204-47cf-9ce4-96d996c96142/language/en-US/Default.aspx|title=Kiribati 1 - 17 Papua New Guinea|author=|date=3 September 2011|work=oceaniafootball.com|publisher=Oceania Football Confederation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130210163731/http://www.oceaniafootball.com/ofc/News/ViewArticle/tabid/125/Article/22e56dd4-4204-47cf-9ce4-96d996c96142/language/en-US/Default.aspx|archivedate=10 February 2013|deadurl=yes|accessdate=25 May 2013|df=}}</ref> and a 9-0 loss to [[Fiji national football team|Fiji]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oceaniafootball.com/ofc/News/ViewArticle/tabid/125/Article/9da7e00d-a5b0-4990-9f93-462f2a9238c5/language/en-US/Default.aspx |title=Fiji 9 - 0 Kiribati |author= |date=30 August 2011 |work=oceaniafootball.com |publisher=Oceania Football Confederation |accessdate=25 May 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130210164136/http://www.oceaniafootball.com/ofc/News/ViewArticle/tabid/125/Article/9da7e00d-a5b0-4990-9f93-462f2a9238c5/language/en-US/Default.aspx |archivedate=10 February 2013 |df= }}</ref>
