{{About|the men's team|the women's team|Kyrgyzstan women's national rugby union team}}

The '''Kyrgyzstan national rugby union team''' represents [[Kyrgyzstan]] in international [[rugby union]]. Although the nation is a member of the [[International Rugby Board]] (IRB) it has not played in a [[Rugby World Cup]] tournament.

