'''Olimpi Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Tbilisi]], [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]].  It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[FC Tbilisi]]. The stadium is able to hold 3,000 people.

