==Shooting== {{main article|Shooting at the 2004 Summer Olympics}} Shooting was San Marino's strongest sport of the Athens games. Amici was just two shots short of qualifying for the final, while Felici was even closer, managing to force a shoot-off and missing out by just a single point.
